{
  "id": "5c50fbfda3e5e7001707937e",
  "title": "事実確認的と行為遂行的",
  "created": 1548811271,
  "updated": 1553522678,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c50fbfda3e5e7001707937e",
      "text": "事実確認的と行為遂行的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811271,
      "updated": 1548811274
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fc3caff09e0000bab40d",
      "text": "\t[言語行為論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811324,
      "updated": 1548811330
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fc15aff09e0000bab40a",
      "text": " \t[事実確認的]([constavive])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811285,
      "updated": 1548811327
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fc19aff09e0000bab40c",
      "text": " \t[行為遂行的]([performative])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811290,
      "updated": 1548811327
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8778d6aff09e00008308e8",
      "text": " \t[Ｊ・Ｌ・オースティン]による分類",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552382166,
      "updated": 1552382191
    },
    {
      "id": "5c98df45aff09e0000b434e8",
      "text": " >従来の言語論が命題の真偽を主として問題にしてきたのに対し，文の発話は同時に行為の遂行となっていると指摘した。たとえば「約束する」と発話することは，すなわち「約束」という行為を行うことにほかならない。このように何かを語ることによって執行される行為を「発話内行為」という。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553522501,
      "updated": 1553522524
    },
    {
      "id": "5c98df5caff09e0000b434e9",
      "text": " \tブリタニカ国際大百科事典 小項目事典",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1553522525,
      "updated": 1553522541
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fc17aff09e0000bab40b",
      "text": "\tある文章をどちらで解釈すべきかは、形式的な解析ではわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811288,
      "updated": 1548811398
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fc83aff09e0000bab40e",
      "text": "\tすべての命題は行為遂行的な読みに開かれている＝意味が確定しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811398,
      "updated": 1548811430
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fca5aff09e0000bab40f",
      "text": "\t\t→コミュニケーションに支障が出る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811430,
      "updated": 1548811437
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fcacaff09e0000bab410",
      "text": "\t\t事実確認的にしか受け取らない領域（例：学会）",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811437,
      "updated": 1548811477
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fcd4aff09e0000bab414",
      "text": "\t\t解釈を安定させる社会的装置",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811477,
      "updated": 1548811477
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fcd5aff09e0000bab415",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811477,
      "updated": 1548811478
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fcfdaff09e0000bab418",
      "text": "2通りの意見",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811517,
      "updated": 1548811520
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fce7aff09e0000bab416",
      "text": "\t[対話]とは合理的で論理的な意見交換であるべき",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811495,
      "updated": 1552153840
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd05aff09e0000bab419",
      "text": "\t\t命題の解釈を事実確認的水準に限定したうえで行わなければいけない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811526,
      "updated": 1548811530
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fce8aff09e0000bab417",
      "text": "\tある特定の解釈の水準を標準的だと決定することは「[規則設定の暴力]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811497,
      "updated": 1553522656
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd1daff09e0000bab41a",
      "text": "\t\t[ベンヤミン]の『[暴力批判論]』以来さんざん言われていること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811549,
      "updated": 1548811559
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd27aff09e0000bab41b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811559,
      "updated": 1548811560
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd60aff09e0000bab421",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811617,
      "updated": 1548811617
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd59aff09e0000bab41c",
      "text": "\tミハイル・バフチン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811610,
      "updated": 1548811621
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd64aff09e0000bab422",
      "text": "\t\t対話を、事実遂行的な命題の交換ではなく、行為遂行的な命題のバトルとして考えた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811621,
      "updated": 1548811627
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd70aff09e0000bab424",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811632,
      "updated": 1548811632
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd6baff09e0000bab423",
      "text": "\t[言語行為論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811627,
      "updated": 1548811642
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd8aaff09e0000bab429",
      "text": "\t\t必読",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811658,
      "updated": 1548811660
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd7aaff09e0000bab425",
      "text": " \t\t[Ｊ・Ｌ・オースティン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811642,
      "updated": 1548811661
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd7daff09e0000bab426",
      "text": " \t\t[ジョン・サール]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811645,
      "updated": 1548811661
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd81aff09e0000bab427",
      "text": " \t\t[サールとデリダの論争]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811650,
      "updated": 1548811661
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd86aff09e0000bab428",
      "text": "\t\t[ベイトソン]の[ダブルバインド]論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811655,
      "updated": 1548811675
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd9aaff09e0000bab42a",
      "text": "\t\t応用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811675,
      "updated": 1548811677
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fd9caff09e0000bab42b",
      "text": "\t\t\t[バフチン]の[ポリフォニー]論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811677,
      "updated": 1548811682
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fda2aff09e0000bab42c",
      "text": "\t\t\t[フーコーのパイプ]の論文",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811682,
      "updated": 1548811690
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fdaaaff09e0000bab42d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811691,
      "updated": 1548811692
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fcb3aff09e0000bab411",
      "text": "参考元: https://togetter.com/li/840705",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811444,
      "updated": 1553522678
    },
    {
      "id": "5c50fc11aff09e0000bab409",
      "text": "\t「理系と文系」みたいな分け方はあまり好きではないので削った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548811281,
      "updated": 1552153825
    },
    {
      "id": "5c83fcd5aff09e0000586618",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552153813,
      "updated": 1552153813
    }
  ]
}